'''ZTE Open'''是由[[中興通訊|中興通訊]]所推出的[[Firefox_OS|Firefox OS]][[智慧型手機|智慧型手機]]。此款手機只針對開發者用於開發和測試，於[[西班牙|西班牙]]率先正式展開銷售<ref name="infoworld">{{cite web |title = Review: Firefox OS sputters on the ZTE Open | Mobile Technology - InfoWorld |url = http://www.infoworld.com/d/mobile-technology/review-firefox-os-sputters-the-zte-open-225794?page=0,1 |first = Galen |last = Gruman |publisher = Infoworld.com |date = 29 August 2013 |accessdate = 22 September 2013 |archive-date = 2021-03-12 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210312071312/https://www.infoworld.com/article/2611825/review--firefox-os-sputters-on-the-zte-open.html |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="pof">{{cite web |url = http://pof.eslack.org/2013/07/05/zte-open-firefoxos-phone-root-and-first-impressions/ |title = ZTE Open FirefoxOS Phone, root and first impressions | pofHQ |first = Pau Oliva |last = Fora |date = 5 July 2013 |publisher = Pof.eslack.org |accessdate = 14 October 2013 |archive-date = 2021-03-12 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210312071257/https://googleads.g.doubleclick.net/pagead/html/r20210309/r20190131/zrt_lookup.html |dead-url = no }}</ref>。

==历史==
2013年8月12日，ZTE Open於[[美國|美國]]和[[英國|英國]]的[[eBay|eBay]]上販售<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ztedevice.com/news/company_news/bb874d58-5a32-4e65-b075-32f5f0959d16.html |title=ZTE to sell ZTE Open Firefox OS phone on eBay US and UK |accessdate=2013-08-12 |archive-date=2016-03-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160313020514/http://www.ztedevice.com/news/company_news/bb874d58-5a32-4e65-b075-32f5f0959d16.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，上架開賣一周內全數迅速銷售一空<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.zdnet.com/article/next-batch-of-ztes-sold-out-firefox-os-smartphones-coming-in-september/ |title=Next batch of ZTE's sold-out Firefox OS smartphones coming in September |accessdate=2013-08-21 |archive-date=2020-10-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201023041912/https://www.zdnet.com/article/next-batch-of-ztes-sold-out-firefox-os-smartphones-coming-in-september/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.techradar.com/news/phone-and-communications/mobile-phones/first-run-of-firefox-os-powered-zte-open-smartphones-sold-out-1174799 |title=First run of Firefox OS-powered ZTE Open smartphones sell out |accessdate=2013-08-21 |archive-date=2021-03-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210328034927/https://www.techradar.com/news/phone-and-communications/mobile-phones/first-run-of-firefox-os-powered-zte-open-smartphones-sold-out-1174799 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。10月15日，ZTE Open於eBay上販售範圍開放至更多地區，包含[[日本|日本]]、[[南韓|南韓]]、[[印尼|印尼]]、[[台灣|台灣]]、[[新加坡|新加坡]]、[[澳門|澳門]]、[[馬來西亞|馬來西亞]]、[[菲律賓|菲律賓]]、[[泰國|泰國]]、[[越南|越南]]、[[寮國|寮國]]、[[汶萊|汶萊]]、[[澳洲|澳洲]]和[[紐西蘭|紐西蘭]]等<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://blog.mozilla.com.tw/posts/3959/3959 |title=存档副本 |access-date=2014-01-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140102192413/http://blog.mozilla.com.tw/posts/3959/3959 |archive-date=2014-01-02 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。10月25日，中興通訊與印度eBay（eBay.in）合作販售ZTE Open<ref name="Evyush.com">{{cite web | title = Firefox phone ZTE Open launches in India, limited units available | url = http://www.evyush.com/mobile-devices/firefox-phone-zte-open-launches-india-limited-units/1669/ | publisher = Evyush.com | date = 26 October 2013 | access-date = 2014-01-01 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20131029002700/http://www.evyush.com/mobile-devices/firefox-phone-zte-open-launches-india-limited-units/1669/ | archive-date = 2013-10-29 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>，定價為6,990[[盧比|盧比]]（111[[美元|美元]]）<ref>{{cite web |url=http://gadgets.ndtv.com/mobiles/news/zte-open-firefox-os-phone-available-online-for-rs-6990-437343 |title=ZTE Open Firefox OS phone available online for Rs. 6,990 |accessdate=2013-10-25 |archive-date=2020-08-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200805024516/https://gadgets.ndtv.com/mobiles/news/zte-open-firefox-os-phone-available-online-for-rs-6990-437343 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

